text: Takheun bak Tuhan tamohon bagah Tamohon duʻa bak Tuhan Rahman Sipheut Droeuneuhnyan nyang Maha Murah Peue nyang talakee bak tameudu‘a Sit le that nama nyang jroh keu Allah Bak tameuduʻa teuma di gata Su bek that raya hana phaedah f Teuma bek cit that halon tameusu Rayok sigitu meubek that leupah Diantaranyan tadeungo keudroe
